The RTAViewer visualize the triggered telescope.

Requires the following python packages in order to run:
  root-python
  numpy
  chaco
  pyfits

You need to download a root file with telescopes informations and place within the RTAViewer.py folder. It must be named Aar.prod2.a2.root in order to work.

To launch the viewer just run:
  $ ./RTAViewer

Then use a client application that sends informations to this viewer (like RTAReceiver_Ice).
